OL,3,CHow involved is the UK in Trump's war
OL,4,Cwith Iran?
OL,6,FYou might have missed it if you
OL,7,Fweren't following the news this
OL,8,Fweekend, but there was a moment when
OL,9,FBritain wasn't involved in this war.
OL,11,FThe US-Israeli airstrikes started at
OL,12,F6.30am on Saturday, but the UK did not
OL,13,Ftake part.
OL,15,FIn fact the prime minister had turned
OL,16,Fdown an American request to allow
OL,17,Ftheir bombers to fly from RAF Fairford
OL,18,Fin Gloucestershire and the base at
OL,19,FDiego Garcia in the Indian Ocean.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
