OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772503387
OL,3,CHow involved is the UK in Trump's war
OL,4,Cwith Iran?
OL,6,FThe UK didn't think the US had a legal
OL,7,Fcase for launching airstrikes as Iran
OL,8,Fhad not launched military strikes
OL,9,Fitself and there was no evidence that
OL,10,Fit was about to.
OL,12,FLater the prime minister said, "I want
OL,13,Fto be very clear: we all remember the
OL,14,Fmistakes of Iraq. And we have learned
OL,15,Fthose lessons.
OL,17,F"We were not involved in the initial
OL,18,Fstrikes on Iran and we will not join
OL,19,Foffensive action now."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
