OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772503387
OL,3,CHow involved is the UK in Trump's war
OL,4,Cwith Iran?
OL,6,FBut by Saturday afternoon the Iranians
OL,7,Fwere lashing out across the region,
OL,8,Fattacking countries which had not been
OL,9,Finvolved in the morning's strikes, and
OL,10,Fthat changed things.
OL,12,FThe RAF was now starting to fly
OL,13,Fdefensive missions from Cyprus and
OL,14,FQatar to intercept drone attacks, and
OL,15,Fa British counter-drone unit shot down
OL,16,Fa drone heading for a base in Iraq.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
