OL,3,CHow involved is the UK in Trump's war
OL,4,Cwith Iran?
OL,6,FSo on Sunday the prime minister
OL,7,Fconfirmed the UK had shifted its
OL,8,Fposition: The Americans would be
OL,9,Fallowed to fly missions against Iran
OL,10,Ffrom British bases.
OL,12,FIn a late night statement, Keir
OL,13,FStarmer said: "The basis of our
OL,14,Fdecision is the collective self-
OL,15,Fdefence of longstanding friends and
OL,16,Fallies, and protecting British lives.
OL,18,F"That is in accordance with
OL,19,Finternational law."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
