OL,3,CHow involved is the UK in Trump's war
OL,4,Cwith Iran?
OL,6,FWhat that means is that the US can
OL,7,Fattack the Iranian ballistic missile
OL,8,Fdepots and launchers which threaten
OL,9,Fthe UK's allies and the 200,000
OL,10,FBritons thought to be in the region.
OL,12,FJoint US-UK targeting boards will
OL,13,Fapprove these missions.
OL,15,FOnce those missiles are destroyed -
OL,16,Fand there are understood to be a
OL,17,Flimited number of them - then in
OL,18,Ftheory that permission ends.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
