OL,3,CHow involved is the UK in Trump's war
OL,4,Cwith Iran?
OL,6,FAlthough the UK is still not flying
OL,7,Fmissions against Iran directly, the
OL,8,Fcountry's deputy foreign minister told
OL,9,FITV News that Starmer was "actively
OL,10,Fparticipating in this aggression".
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe moment in which it denied US
OL,18,Fflights from British bases was barely
OL,19,F36 hours long.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
