FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772503387
OL,3,CHow involved is the UK in Trump's war
OL,4,Cwith Iran?
OL,6,FBut President Trump has already said
OL,7,Fit "took far too long" and he is "very
OL,8,Fdisappointed" in Keir Starmer.
OL,10,F"President Trump has expressed his
OL,11,Fdisagreement with our decision not to
OL,12,Fget involved in the initial strikes,"
OL,13,FStarmer told the Commons on Monday.
OL,14,F"But it is my duty to judge what is in
OL,15,FBritain's national interest."
OL,17,FThe bit of the weekend you could
OL,18,Feasily have missed may yet turn out to
OL,19,Fbe a very big moment in UK-US
OL,20,Frelations.
